6. Implement Rate Limiting

â€¢	Use rate limiting to prevent abuse and mitigate Denial of Service (DoS) attacks.
Example: Using Istio for Rate Limiting

apiVersion: config.istio.io/v1alpha2
kind: QuotaSpec
metadata:
  name: request-count
  namespace: your-namespace
spec:
  rules:
  - quotas:
    - charge: 1
      quota: requestcount

